https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/','Supercache Uninstall Problems'=>'Supercache 卸载问题','Cleaning up old supercache files.'=>'正在清理过期的 supercache 文件。','[%s] Cache Preload Completed'=>'[%s] 预缓存完成','Scheduling next preload refresh in %d minutes.'=>'下次预缓存任务将在%d分后开始。','Refreshed the following posts:'=>'以下文章已被刷新：','[%1$s] %2$d posts refreshed'=>'[%1$s] %2$d 篇文章已刷新','[%1$s] Cache Preload Stopped'=>'[%1$s] 预缓存已停止','[%1$s] Refreshing posts from %2$d to %3$d'=>'[%1$s] 正在刷新从 %2$d 到 %3$d 的文章','[%1$s] Refreshing %2$s taxonomy from %3$d to %4$d'=>'[%1$s] 正在刷新 从 %3$d 到 %4$d 的 %2$s 分类法','[%1$s] Cache Preload Started'=>'[%1$s] 预缓存已开始','Update Mod_Rewrite Rules'=>'更新 Mod_Rewrite 规则',' Make sure they appear before any existing WordPress rules. '=>' 确保它们在已有的 WordPress 规则前。','You can edit the file yourself. Add the following rules.'=>'您可以自己编辑该文件。添加下面的规则。','To serve static html files your server must have the correct mod_rewrite rules added to a file called <code>%s.htaccess</code>'=>'如果要使缓存页面生效，您的服务器必须要有包含正确的 mod_rewrite 规则的 <code>%s.htaccess</code> 文件','Alternatively, you can edit your <code>%s.htaccess</code> file manually and add the following code (before any WordPress rules):'=>'另外，您还可以自行编辑您的 <code>%s.htaccess</code> 文件并添加以下代码 (在任何 WordPress 规则之前):','Refresh this page when the file permissions have been modified.'=>'当文件权限更改后请刷新本页。','The file <code>%s.htaccess</code> cannot be modified by the web server. Please correct this using the chmod command or your ftp client.'=>'<code>%s.htaccess</code> 文件无法被服务器变更。请使用 chmod 命令或 ftp 客户端来修正权限。','Cannot update .htaccess'=>'无法更新 .htaccess 文件','WP Super Cache has checked the front page of your blog. Please visit %s if you would like to disable this.'=>'WP Super Cache 已经检查您的博客的首页。如果您想禁用，请访问 %s 。','[%s] Front page check!'=>'[%s] 首页检查！','The cache on your blog has been cleared because the front page of your site is missing the text "%2$s". Please visit %1$s to verify the cache has been cleared.'=>'由于首页缺失 "%2$s" ，所有缓存已被清除。请访问 %1$s 以检查缓存是否已被清除。','[%s] Front page is not correct! Cache Cleared!'=>'[%s] 首页不正确！缓存已清除！','Please visit %1$s to clear the cache as the front page of your site is not correct and missing the text, "%2$s"!'=>'请访问 %1$s 以清除您的站点的首页缓存，该缓存是错误的或者缺失文字 "%2$s"！','[%s] Front page is not correct! Please clear cache!'=>'[%s] 首页不正确！请清除缓存！','The cache on your blog has been cleared because the front page of your site is now downloading. Please visit %s to verify the cache has been cleared.'=>'由于首页正在被加载，您的博客的所有缓存已被清除。请访问 %s 以检查缓存是否已被清除。','[%s] Front page is gzipped! Cache Cleared!'=>'[%s] 首页已被 gzip 压缩！缓存已清除！','Please visit %s to clear the cache as the front page of your site is now downloading!'=>'由于您的首页正在被加载，请自行访问 %s 以清除首页的缓存！','[%s] Front page is gzipped! Please clear cache!'=>'[%s] 首页已经被 gzip 压缩！请清除缓存！','Warning! WP Super Cache caching <strong>was</strong> broken but has been <strong>fixed</strong>! The script advanced-cache.php could not load wp-cache-phase1.php.<br /><br />The file %1$s/advanced-cache.php has been recreated and WPCACHEHOME fixed in your wp-config.php. Reload to hide this message.'=>'警告！WP Super Cache缓存<strong>被打破</strong> ，但<strong>已修复</strong>！该脚本advanced-cache.php无法加载WP-cache-phase1.php。 <br /><br />wp-config.php文件中的 %1$s/advanced-cache.php已被重新创建并且WPCACHEHOME已被修复。刷新可隐藏此消息。','WP Super Cache is disabled. Please go to the <a href="%s">plugin admin page</a> to enable caching.'=>'WP Super Cache 已禁用。请去 <a href="%s">插件管理首页</a> 开启缓存功能。','Settings'=>'设置','WP Super Cache must be configured. Go to <a href="%s">the admin page</a> to enable and configure the plugin.'=>'WP Super Cache 需要设置。请前往 <a href="%s">插件管理页面</a> 设置。','Delete Super Cache cached files (opens in new window)'=>'删除 Super Cache 插件的缓存文件 (新窗口中打开)','Delete Expired'=>'删除已过期文件','Expired files are files older than %s seconds. They are still used by the plugin and are deleted periodically.'=>'到期文件是那些存在时间大于%s秒的文件。它们仍在被调用并会定期被删除。','List all cached files'=>'列出所有已缓存的文件','Too many cached files, no listing possible.'=>'缓存文件太多，没有列表可用。','Hide file list'=>'隐藏文件列表','Delete'=>'删除','Age'=>'有效时间','URI'=>'URI','WP-Super-Cache'=>'WP-Super-Cache','%s Expired Pages'=>'%s 已过期页面','%s Cached Pages'=>'%s 已缓存页面','WP-Cache'=>'WP-Cache','Cache stats last generated: %s minutes ago.'=>'缓存统计已于 %s分钟前生成。','Regenerate cache stats'=>'重新生成缓存统计信息','Cache stats are not automatically generated. You must click the link below to regenerate the stats on this page.'=>'缓存统计信息不是自动生成的，您需要点击下面的链接来重新生成。','Deleting wp-cache file: <strong>%s</strong><br />'=>'正在删除 wp-cache 的相关文件： <strong>%s</strong><br />','Deleting supercache file: <strong>%s</strong><br />'=>'正在删除 supercache 的相关文件： <strong>%s</strong><br />','Cache Contents'=>'缓存内容','<h4>WP_CACHE constant added to wp-config.php</h4><p>If you continue to see this warning message please see point 5 of the <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/faq/">Troubleshooting Guide</a>. The WP_CACHE line must be moved up.'=>'<h4>WP_CACHE常量添加到wp-config.php</h4><p>如果您继续看到此警告消息，请参阅<a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/faq/">故障排除指南</a>的第5点。 必须向上移动WP_CACHE行。','Edit <code>%s</code> and add the following line:<br /> <code>define(\'WP_CACHE\', true);</code><br />Otherwise, <strong>WP-Cache will not be executed</strong> by WordPress core. '=>'编辑 <code>%s</code> 并添加如下内容：<br /> <code>define(\'WP_CACHE\', true);</code><br /否则，<strong>WP-Cache 将不会被执行</strong>。','<strong>Error: WP_CACHE is not enabled</strong> in your <code>wp-config.php</code> file and I couldn&#8217;t modify it.'=>'<strong>错误：您的 <code>wp-config.php</code> 文件中 WP_CACHE 未被启用</strong> 并且插件无法变更。','<h4>WP_CACHE constant set to false</h4><p>The WP_CACHE constant is used by WordPress to load the code that serves cached pages. Unfortunately, it is set to false. Please edit your wp-config.php and add or edit the following line above the final require_once command:<br /><br /><code>define(\'WP_CACHE\', true);</code></p>'=>'<h4>WP_CACHE常量设置为false</h4><p>WordPress使用WP_CACHE常量来加载提供缓存页面的代码。 不幸的是，它被设置为false。 请编辑你的wp-config.php并在最终的require_once命令上面添加或编辑以下行：<br /><br /><code>define(\'WP_CACHE\', true);</code></p>','If that doesn&#8217;t work, make sure the file <em>%s/advanced-cache.php</em> doesn&#8217;t exist:'=>'如果不能工作，请确保文件 <em>%s/advanced-cache.php</em> 不存在：','Refresh this page to update <em>%s/advanced-cache.php</em>'=>'刷新本页以便更新 <em>%s/advanced-cache.php</em>','Make %1$s writable using the chmod command through your ftp or server software. (<em>chmod 777 %1$s</em>) and refresh this page. This is only a temporary measure and you&#8217;ll have to make it read only afterwards again. (Change 777 to 755 in the previous command)'=>'将 %1$s 通过 chmod 或者 ftp 客户端设置为可被写入(<em>chmod 777 %1$s</em>) 并刷新本页。这只是一个临时的操作，您需要随后恢复该文件之前的只读权限。(将之前括号内的777改为755，并执行修改后的命令)','Could not update %s!</em> WPCACHEHOME must be set in config file.'=>'无法更新 %s！必须设置</em> WPCACHEHOME。','Sample WP-Cache config file (<strong>%s</strong>) does not exist. Verify your installation.'=>'样品WP-Cache配置文件<strong>（%s）</strong>不存在。检查您的验证。','Configuration file missing and %1$s  directory (<strong>%2$s</strong>) is not writable by the web server. Check its permissions.'=>'配置文件丢失，%1$s目录（<strong>%2$s</strong>）不是Web服务器可写的。请检查它的权限。','Your WP-Cache config file (<strong>%s</strong>) is out of date and not writable by the Web server. Please delete it and refresh this page.'=>'您的WP-Cache配置文件(<strong>%s</strong>) 已过时，而不是由Web服务器可写的。请删除它，并刷新此页面。','Your cache directory (<strong>%1$s</strong>) or <strong>%2$s</strong> need to be writable for this plugin to work. Double-check it.'=>'您的缓存目录 (<strong>%1$s</strong>) 或者 <strong>%2$s</strong>需要被设置为可写入权限。请检查有关设置。','Your cache directory (<strong>%1$s</strong>) did not exist and couldn&#8217;t be created by the web server. Check %1$s permissions.'=>'您的缓存目录 (<strong>%1$s</strong>) 不存在且 Web 服务器无法创建。请检查 %1$s 的权限设置。','Error'=>'错误','GZIP compression is enabled in WordPress, wp-cache will be bypassed until you disable gzip compression.'=>'WordPress 已启用 GZIP 压缩，wp-cache 将会自动忽略直到您禁用 gzip 压缩。','Warning'=>'警告','Email the blog admin when checks are made. (useful for testing)'=>'当有检查时发送邮件提醒站点管理员。(对测试十分有用)','Clear cache on error.'=>'出错时清除缓存。','Text to search for on your front page. If this text is missing, the cache will be cleared. Leave blank to disable.'=>'搜索您的首页有文字。如果不填该处文字，缓存将被清除。留空以禁用。','Front page text'=>'首页文字','Check front page every 5 minutes.'=>'每5分钟检查一次首页。','I&#8217;m 99% certain that they aren&#8217;t bugs in WP Super Cache and they only happen in very rare cases but you can run a simple check once every 5 minutes to verify that your site is ok if you&#8217;re worried. You will be emailed if there is a problem.'=>'我有 99% 的把握：这不是 WP Super Cache 的 Bug，这种情况只会在极其罕见的情况下发生。如果您仍然不放心，我建议您每5分钟做一次对站点的简单检查，以便验证站点是否运行正常。如果产生任何问题，您会收到系统发送的邮件通知。','In very rare cases two problems may arise on some blogs:<ol><li> The front page may start downloading as a zip file.</li><li> The wrong page is occasionally cached as the front page if your blog uses a static front page and the permalink structure is <em>/%category%/%postname%/</em>.</li></ol>'=>'在某些情况下，有以下2个问题可能会发生：<ol><li>加载首页时会变成 zip 档案下载。</li><li> 如果您的博客使用静态首页，并且固定链接结构类似于 <em>/%category%/%postname%/</em> ，某些错误的页面会被当做首页进行缓存。</li></ol>','Display comments at the end of every page like this:'=>'像这样的方式显示每页末尾的评论：','Cache Status Messages'=>'缓存状态消息','(only log requests from this IP address. Your IP is %s)'=>'(仅记录来自该 IP 的请求，您的 IP 是 %s)','IP Address'=>'IP 地址','Fix problems with the plugin by debugging it here. It will log to a file in your cache directory.'=>'通过在这里调试来修复故障，调试功能会在缓存文件目录下生成日志。','Currently logging to: %s'=>'目前正在登录：%s','Save Files'=>'保存文件','Add here those filenames that can be cached, even if they match one of the rejected substring specified above.'=>'添加想要被缓存的文件名，即使它们出现在上面的被拒绝列表里面。','Save Strings'=>'保存','Add here strings (not a filename) that forces a page not to be cached. For example, if your URLs include year and you dont want to cache last year posts, it&#8217;s enough to specify the year, i.e. &#8217;/2004/&#8217;. WP-Cache will search if that string is part of the URI and if so, it will not cache that page.'=>'在这里添加强制禁止缓存的页面的地址关键字。例如，如果您的地址包含年份并且您不想缓存上一年的文章，您可以直接填写 &#8217;/2004/&#8217;。WP-Cache 将会搜索所有符合条件的页面并且不缓存它们。','Save'=>'保存','Author Pages'=>'作者页面','Search Pages'=>'搜索页面','Feeds'=>'Feeds','Category'=>'分类','Tags'=>'标签','Archives'=>'存档','Home'=>'主页','Front Page'=>'首页','Pages'=>'页面','Single Posts'=>'单一文章','Do not cache the following page types. See the <a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Conditional_Tags">Conditional Tags</a> documentation for a complete discussion on each type.'=>'不要缓存例如下列格式的页面。请见 <a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Conditional_Tags">Conditional Tags</a> 文档查看所有格式的具体说明。','Save UA Strings'=>'保存用户代理(UA)字段','Strings in the HTTP &#8217;User Agent&#8217; header that prevent WP-Cache from caching bot, spiders, and crawlers&#8217; requests. Note that super cached files are still sent to these agents if they already exists.'=>'HTTP &#8217中的字符串；浏览器&#8217; 防止WP-Cache缓存网络机器人的http头, 蜘蛛, 网络爬虫&#8217;的请求。请注意超级缓存文件仍然会被发送给这些代理。','Rejected User Agents'=>'已拒绝的用户代理(User Agent)','Change Expiration'=>'修改过期设置','Set the expiry time to 0 seconds to disable garbage collection.'=>'设置到期时间为0秒以便禁用垃圾回收器。','Sites where an external data source updates at a particular time every day should set the timeout to 86400 seconds and use the Clock scheduler set appropriately.'=>'每天有固定更新产生的站点应该设缓存超时时间为86400秒并正确设置时钟时间。','Sites with lots of static content, no widgets or rss feeds in their sidebar can use a timeout of 86400 seconds or even more and set the timer to something equally long.'=>'有大量静态内容且在侧边栏没有挂件和 rss 输出的站点，应该设置超时时间为86400秒或更长并设置定时器为一个很长的时间。','Sites with widgets and rss feeds in their sidebar should probably use a timeout of 3600 seconds and set the timer to 600 seconds. Stale files will be caught within 10 minutes of going stale.'=>'在侧边栏有挂件和 rss 输出的站点应该设置超时时间为3600秒，并设置定时器为600秒。过期缓存将会在10分钟内随时被收集。','Sites that want to serve lots of newly generated data should set the <em>Cache Timeout</em> to 60 and use the <em>Timer</em> scheduler set to 90 seconds.'=>'有大量新数据产生的站点应该设置<em>缓存超时时间</em>为60并设置<em>定时器</em>时间为90秒。','There are no best garbage collection settings but here are a few scenarios. Garbage collection is separate to other actions that clear our cached files like leaving a comment or publishing a post.'=>'没有十分完美的垃圾回收器设置，不过它已被单独分离出来，这样清理缓存文件就像留下一条评论或者发布文章一样简单。','Or, the <em>Clock</em> scheduler allows the garbage collection to run at specific times. If set to run hourly or twice daily, the garbage collector will be first scheduled for the time you enter here. It will then run again at the indicated interval. If set to run daily, it will run once a day at the time specified.'=>'或者，<em>定时</em>计划程序允许垃圾回收在特定时间运行。如果设置为每小时一次或两次运行，垃圾收集器将首先安排您在此处输入的时间。然后它会在指定的时间再次运行。如果设置为每天运行，它会每天在指定时间运行一次。','The <em>Timer</em> scheduler tells the plugin to run the garbage collector at regular intervals. When one garbage collection is done, the next run is scheduled.'=>'<em>定时器</em> 告诉插件间隔多久运行垃圾回收器。当一次回收完毕时，下次任务将会被设计划。','Use the <em>Timer</em> or <em>Clock</em> schedulers to define when the garbage collector should run.'=>'使用 <em>定时器</em> 或 <em>时钟</em> 选项来设定垃圾回收器何时应该运行。','Stale cached files are not removed as soon as they become stale. They have to be removed by the garbage collecter. That is why you have to tell the plugin when the garbage collector should run.'=>'过期的缓存文件并会被立刻删除。它们会被垃圾回收器清除。这就是您需要对垃圾回收器进行配置的原因。','Cached files are fresh for a limited length of time. You can set that time in the <em>Cache Timeout</em> text box on this page.'=>'缓存都是有一定的新鲜时间的，您可以在本页的 <em>缓存过期时间</em> 文本框进行设置。','<em>Garbage collection</em> is the simple act of throwing out your garbage. For this plugin that would be old or <em>stale</em> cached files that may be out of date. New cached files are described as <em>fresh</em>.'=>'<em>垃圾回收器</em> 是一个减少垃圾的工具。因为插件产生的缓存会随着时间推移而<em>过期</em>，因此新生成的缓存文件因此是<em>新鲜</em>的。','Garbage Collection'=>'垃圾回收器','Email me when the garbage collection runs.'=>'当垃圾回收器运行时发送邮件通知我。','Notification Emails'=>'邮件通知','Interval:'=>'任务间隔：','Check for stale cached files at this time <strong>(UTC)</strong> or starting at this time every <em>interval</em> below.'=>'每当到了您设定的 <strong>(UTC)</strong> 时间或者任务间隔检查过期的缓存文件。','HH:MM'=>'小时:分钟','Clock:'=>'时间：','Timer:'=>'定时器:','Scheduler'=>'计划','How long should cached pages remain fresh? Set to 0 to disable garbage collection. A good starting point is 3600 seconds.'=>'哪些缓存页面是没有过期的？设置为0可以禁用垃圾回收器。建议数值为3600。','seconds'=>'秒','Cache Timeout'=>'缓存超时时间','Warning! <strong>PRELOAD MODE</strong> activated. Supercache files will not be deleted regardless of age.'=>'警告！<strong>预缓存模式</strong> 已激活！Supercache 的缓存文件由于缓存的有效时间而不会被删除。','Next scheduled garbage collection will be at <strong>%s UTC</strong>'=>'下次垃圾收集计划任务将会在 <strong>%s UTC</strong> 开始','Local time is <code>%1$s</code>'=>'本地时间是 <code>%1$s</code>','<abbr title="Coordinated Universal Time">UTC</abbr> time is <code>%s</code>'=>'<abbr title="Coordinated Universal Time">UTC</abbr>时间是<code>%s</code>','Expiry Time &amp; Garbage Collection'=>'到期时间和垃圾回收器','timezone date formatY-m-d G:i:s'=>'Y-m-d G:i:s','Update Direct Pages'=>'更新直接链接页面','Make the textbox blank to remove it from the list of direct pages and delete the cached file.'=>'如果文本框留空，将会移除直接页面列表中内容的并删除缓存文件。','For example: to cache <em>%1$sabout/</em>, you would enter %1$sabout/ or /about/. The cached file will be generated the next time an anonymous user visits that page.'=>'例如：为了缓存 <em>%1$sabout/</em>，您需要访问 %1$sabout/ 或 /about/。缓存文件将会在下次匿名用户来访时再次生成。','Directly cached files are files created directly off %s where your blog lives. This feature is only useful if you are expecting a major Digg or Slashdot level of traffic to one post or page.'=>'直接缓存文件是直接由你博客所处的%s所创建的文件。如果你期待一个文章或页面的访客达到Digg或Slashdot的水平，，此功能才有用。','Add direct page:'=>'添加跳转页面(Direct Page)：','Delete cached file'=>'删除已缓存文件','Existing direct page'=>'已存在的跳转页面','%s is writable. Please make it readonly after your page is generated as this is a security risk.'=>'%s 可被写入。由于存在安全风险，请在页面生成后设置为只读权限。','You must make %s writable to enable this feature. As this is a security risk, please make it read-only after your page is generated.'=>'你必须让%s可写入才能启用此功能。由于这是一个安全隐患，您的网页生成后请将其设置为只读模式。','Directly Cached Files'=>'直接缓存的文件','Lock Down'=>'锁定','WordPress is not locked down. New comments will refresh Super Cache static files as normal.'=>'WordPress 没有被锁定。新的评论将会像往常一样刷新 Super Cache 的静态文件。','WordPress is locked down. Super Cache static files will not be deleted when new comments are made.'=>'WordPress 已被锁定。当产生新评论时，Super Cache 的静态文件将不会被检测到。','Sorry. My blog is locked down. Updates will appear shortly'=>'抱歉，本博客目前处于锁定中，稍后会进行更新。','Developers: Make your plugin lock down compatible by checking the "WPLOCKDOWN" constant. The following code will make sure your plugin respects the WPLOCKDOWN setting.'=>'对开发者：为了使您自己的插件与锁定功能兼容，请检查 "WPLOCKDOWN" 常量。以下代码将会确保您的插件遵守 WPLOCKDOWN 设置。','Prepare your server for an expected spike in traffic by enabling the lock down. When this is enabled, new comments on a post will not refresh the cached static files.'=>'如果您启用锁定，那么它将会为站点运行高峰时期做好准备。当这项功能启用时，新评论或文章将不会立即刷新至已缓存的静态文件。','Lock Down:'=>'锁定：','Comment moderation is enabled. Your comment may take some time to appear.'=>'评论审核已启用。您的评论可能需要一段时间后才能被显示。','Restore Default Configuration'=>'恢复默认设置','Fix Configuration'=>'修复设置','Rules must be added to %s too:'=>'规则必须也被添加至 %s ：','View Mod_Rewrite Rules'=>'查看 Mod_Rewrite 规则','A difference between the rules in your .htaccess file and the plugin rewrite rules has been found. This could be simple whitespace differences, but you should compare the rules in the file with those below as soon as possible. Click the &#8217;Update Mod_Rewrite Rules&#8217; button to update the rules.'=>'我们发现了.htaccess文件中的规则和插件重写规则之间的不同。这可能是简单的空白差异，建议你比较文件的规则与下面的内容。点击&#8217;更新Mod_Rewrite的规则&#8217;按钮更新规则。','WP Super Cache mod rewrite rules were detected in your %s.htaccess file.<br /> Click the following link to see the lines added to that file. If you have upgraded the plugin, make sure these rules match.'=>'在%s.htaccess文件中，检测到WP Super Cache的mod_rewrite规则。<br /> 点击下面链接查看添加到该文件中的行。如果您已经升级插件，请确保这些规则相一致。','Mod Rewrite rules must be updated!'=>'Mod Rewrite 规则必须被更新！','%s.htaccess has been updated with the necessary mod_rewrite rules. Please verify they are correct. They should look like this:'=>'%s.htaccess 已经被必需的 mod_rewrite 规则更新。请检查它们是否正确。它们应该看上去这样：','Mod Rewrite rules updated!'=>'Mod Rewrite 规则已更新！','The mod_rewrite rules changed since you last installed this plugin. Unfortunately, you must remove the old supercache rules before the new ones are updated. Refresh this page when you have edited your .htaccess file. If you wish to manually upgrade, change the following line: %1$s so it looks like this: %2$s The only changes are "HTTP_COOKIE" becomes "HTTP:Cookie" and "wordpressuser" becomes "wordpress". This is a WordPress 2.5 change but it&#8217;s backwards compatible with older versions if you&#8217;re brave enough to use them.'=>'自您上次安装该插件之后mod_rewrite规则有变更。你必须删除旧的supercache规则才能更新新的规则。在您编辑.htaccess之后再刷新本页。如果您想手动更新，修改下面这行：%1$s，让它变成这样:%2$s。唯一的变化只是"HTTP_COOKIE"变成"HTTP:Cookie"，"wordpressuser"变成"wordpress"。这是WordPress2.5的变更，但如果你敢于尝试的话，这是向后兼容的。','Thank you for upgrading.'=>'感谢您的升级。','Mod Rewrite Rules'=>'Mod Rewrite 规则','Debug'=>'调试','Plugins'=>'插件兼容','Preload'=>'预缓存','Contents'=>'内容','CDN'=>'CDN','Easy'=>'通用','Available Plugins'=>'可用插件','(may not always be accurate on busy sites)'=>'(在某些繁忙的大型站点上可能会不准确)','Cached %s seconds ago'=>'%s秒前已缓存','Newest Cached Pages:'=>'最新的已缓存页面：','Cached pages since %1$s : <strong>%2$s</strong>'=>'从 %1$s 已缓存的页面：<strong>%2$s</strong>','Rate This Plugin'=>'给插件评个分吧！','Need Help?'=>'需要帮助？','<a href="%s">WP Crontrol</a> is a useful plugin to use when trying to debug garbage collection and preload problems.'=>'<a href="%s">WP Crontrol</a> 是一款调试垃圾回收器和预缓存问题的利器。','Caching is only one part of making a website faster. Here are some other plugins that will help:'=>'缓存只是让站点运行更快的一种方法，这里有一些其它插件提供类似功能：','Recommended Links and Plugins'=>'有用的链接和插件','Delete Cache On All Blogs'=>'删除所有博客上的缓存','Delete Cache'=>'删除缓存','Cached pages are stored on your server as html and PHP files. If you need to delete them, use the button below.'=>'缓存的页面都以html和PHP文件的形式存储在您的服务器。如果您想要删除它们，请使用下面的按钮。','Delete Cached Pages'=>'删除已缓存页面','Test Cache'=>'测试缓存','Send non-secure (non https) request for homepage'=>'发送不安全的(非 https) 首页请求','You should check Page 1 and Page 2 above for errors. Your local server configuration may not allow your website to access itself.'=>'您应该在出错前检查页面1和页面2。您的本地服务器设置可能不允许您的网站读取。','Enable logging on the Debug page here. That should help you track down the problem.'=>'在这里启用调试页面的日志记录。这会帮助您跟踪问题。','Load your homepage in a logged out browser, check the timestamp at the end of the html source. Load the page again and compare the timestamp. Caching is working if the timestamps match.'=>'它会在一个已经登出的浏览器环境中加载首页并检查 html 文件结尾的时间戳，然后再次加载页面并对比时间戳。如果时间戳相符则缓存正在工作。','Things you can do:'=>'您可以做的：','The pages do not match! Timestamps differ or were not found!'=>'页面不相符！时间戳有差异或者不存在！','The timestamps on both pages match!'=>'两个页面的时间戳相符！','Page 2: %s'=>'第二页： %s','Page 1: %s'=>'第一页： %s','Page %d: %d (%s)'=>'页面 %d: %d (%s)','Fetching second copy of %s: '=>'抓取 %s 的第二份缓存拷贝：','FAILED'=>'失败','Fetching first copy of %s: '=>'抓取 %s 的第一份缓存拷贝：','OK'=>'OK','Fetching %s to prime cache: '=>'正在抓取 %s 的初始缓存：','Test your cached website by clicking the test button below.'=>'点击下面的测试按钮测试缓存效果。','Cache Tester'=>'缓存测试','Notice: Simple caching enabled but Supercache mod_rewrite rules from expert mode detected. Cached files will be served using those rules. If your site is working ok, please ignore this message. Otherwise, you can edit the .htaccess file in the root of your install and remove the SuperCache rules.'=>'注意︰ PHP缓存已启用，但检测到Supercache mod_rewrite规则。将使用这些规则提供缓存的文件。如果您的网站工作正常，请忽略此消息。否则为您可以编辑您的安装的根目录中的.htaccess文件并删除SuperCache规则。','Caching Off'=>'禁用缓存功能','Caching On'=>'启用缓存功能','Accepted Filenames &amp; Rejected URIs'=>'已被接受的文件名和拒绝的 URI','Update Status'=>'更新','Need help? Check out <a href="%1$s">the documentation</a>. It includes installation documentation, a FAQ, and Troubleshooting tips. The <a href="%2$s">support forum</a> is also available. Your question may already have been answered.'=>'需要帮助？请查看 <a href="%1$s">文档</a>。其中包括安装文档、常见问题和故障排除提示。<a href="%2$s">支持论坛</a>也可供使用。您的问题可能已经有人回答过了。','Please see the <a href="%1$s/wp-super-cache/readme.txt">readme.txt</a> for instructions on uninstalling this script. Look for the heading, "How to uninstall WP Super Cache".'=>'请查看 <a href="%1$s/wp-super-cache/readme.txt">readme.txt</a> 以了解卸载流程。请在文件中搜索 "How to uninstall WP Super Cache"以便快速浏览。','If uninstalling this plugin, make sure the directory <em>%s</em> is writeable by the webserver so the files <em>advanced-cache.php</em> and <em>cache-config.php</em> can be deleted automatically. (Making sure those files are writeable is probably a good idea!)'=>'如果卸载这个插件，请确保目录<em>%s</em>是有Web服务器写入权限，<em>advanced-cache.php</em>和<em>cache-config.php</em>文件可被自动删除。（建议保持这些文件可写！）','Uninstall this plugin on the plugins page. It will automatically clean up after itself. If manual intervention is required, then simple instructions are provided.'=>'在插件页面上卸载这个插件，它会在结束后自动清理。如果需要手动介入，会有简单说明。','Note:'=>'提示：','<strong>DO NOT CACHE PAGE</strong> secret key: <a href="%s">%s</a>'=>'<strong>访问这个链接将不会显示缓存内容</strong>： <a href="%s">%s</a>','List the newest cached pages on this page.'=>'在该页列出所有最新的缓存页面。','Only refresh current page when comments made.'=>'当某页面有新评论时，只刷新该页面的缓存。','Extra homepage checks. (Very occasionally stops homepage caching)'=>'首页额外检查。 (极少数情况下会停止对首页的缓存)','Clear all cache files when a post or page is published or updated.'=>'当有新文章或页面的发布或更新时清除之前的缓存文件。','Remove UTF8/blog charset support from .htaccess file. Only necessary if you see odd characters or punctuation looks incorrect. Requires rewrite rules update.'=>'移除 .htaccess 文件中的 UTF8/blog 字符集。这个功能只适用于当您发现文件中字符不正确时。本功能需要更新重写规则。','Mobile Prefixes'=>'手机前缀','Mobile Browsers'=>'手机浏览器','Mobile device support. (External plugin or theme required. See the <a href="https://jetpack.com/support/wp-super-cache/wp-super-cache-faq/">FAQ</a> for further details.)'=>'支持移动设备。(需要外部插件或主题。更多详情，请参阅 <a href="https://jetpack.com/support/wp-super-cache/wp-super-cache-faq/"> 常见问题</a>）。','Advanced'=>'高级','Cache rebuild. Serve a supercache file to anonymous users while a new file is being generated.'=>'缓存重建。当新缓存生成时调用缓存文件给匿名用户。','Make known users anonymous so they&#8217;re served supercached static files.'=>'让已知用户匿名使他们浏览的内容是缓存文件。','Don&#8217;t cache pages with GET parameters. (?x=y at the end of a url)'=>'不要为 GET 请求缓存。(地址结尾为?x=y)','304 support is disabled by default because some hosts have had problems with the headers used in the past.'=>'默认情况下禁用304支持，因为某些主机有与过去使用的标头（headers）的问题，','Compression is disabled by default because some hosts have problems with compressed files. Switching it on and off clears the cache.'=>'压缩默认已禁用，因为有些主机对压缩过的文件处理有问题。勾选或取消勾选该功能会清除缓存。','Compress pages so they&#8217;re served more quickly to visitors.'=>'压缩页面以便让来访者更快浏览。','Warning! Compression is disabled as gzencode() function was not found.'=>'警告！ 压缩未启用，因为没找到gzencode() 函数。','Miscellaneous'=>'杂项','Recommended'=>'推荐','Caching'=>'缓存功能','Less emails, 1 at the start and 1 at the end of preloading all posts.'=>'少量邮件，缓存第一篇发送1封邮件，缓存结束时发送再1封邮件。','Medium, 1 email per %d posts.'=>'适量邮件，每 %d 个帖子 1 封电子邮件。','Many emails, 2 emails per %d posts.'=>'大量邮件，每 %d 个帖子 2 封邮件。','Send me status emails when files are refreshed.'=>'当缓存文件刷新完毕后发送邮件通知。','Preload tags, categories and other taxonomies.'=>'预缓存标签，分类以及其他。','Preload %s posts.'=>'预缓存 %s 篇文章。','all'=>'全部','Refresh preloaded cache files every %s minutes. (0 to disable, minimum %d minutes.)'=>'每%s分钟刷新预缓存文件(设置为0则禁用，至少%d分钟。)','Preloading creates lots of files however. Caching is done from the newest post to the oldest so please consider only caching the newest if you have lots (10,000+) of posts. This is especially important on shared hosting.'=>'预缓存将会创建大量新文件，并且会将所有文章进行缓存。如果您有10000篇以上文章，不建议您使用该功能，尤其是在共享主机上。','This will cache every published post and page on your site. It will create supercache static files so unknown visitors (including bots) will hit a cached page. This will probably help your Google ranking as they are using speed as a metric when judging websites now.'=>'预缓存的功能是缓存所有已发布的页面和文章。它会创建 supercache 静态文件，这样的话，未知用户(包括搜索引擎蜘蛛)将会获得缓存后的页面。这将帮助您的站点的 Google PR 提升，因为 Google 会把网站的响应速度作为评判网站的标准。','Preload Cache Now'=>'立即预加载缓存','Cancel Cache Preload'=>'取消预加载缓存','Configuration file changed, some values might be wrong. Load the page again from the "Settings" menu to reset them.'=>'设置文件已变更，有些数值可能是错误的。请通过 "设置" 菜单重新加载。','Notice: <em>Expert mode caching enabled</em>. Showing Advanced Settings Page by default.'=>'注意：由于 <em>Mod_rewrite 模式或者传统模式已启用</em>，默认将显示高级设置选项卡。','<strong>Warning!</strong> You attempted to enable compression but <code>zlib.output_compression</code> is enabled. See #21 in the Troubleshooting section of the readme file.'=>'<strong>警告！</strong>您尝试启用压缩但是 <code>zlib.output_compression</code> 参数已被启用。请查看 readme 文件的疑难问题解决部分的第21号解答。','It appears you have WordPress installed in a sub directory as described <a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Giving_WordPress_Its_Own_Directory">here</a>. Unfortunately, WordPress writes to the .htaccess in the install directory, not where your site is served from.<br />When you update the rewrite rules in this plugin you will have to copy the file to where your site is hosted. This will be fixed in the future.'=>'按<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Giving_WordPress_Its_Own_Directory"></a>描述，您在一个子目录下安装了WordPress。但是WordPress写入的是安装目录下的.htaccess，而不是在你网站目录。<br />当你更新这个插件的重写规则时，你需要复制该文件到您的网站目录。该问题将在未来解决。','.htaccess file may need to be moved'=>'.htaccess文件可能需要被移动','The following Apache modules are missing. The plugin will work in simple mode without them but in expert mode, your visitors may see corrupted pages or out of date content however.'=>'缺少以下Apache模块。 插件将在没有它们的情况下以简单模式工作，但在专家模式下，访客可能会看到损坏的页面或过时的内容。','Missing Apache Modules'=>'找不到 Apache 模块','Set the expiry date on supercached pages. Visitors may not see new pages when they refresh or leave comments without this module.'=>'设定缓存文件的到期时间。没有该模块时，当来访者刷新或者留下评论时可能不会看到新页面。','Required to set caching information on supercache pages. IE7 users will see old pages without this module.'=>'该模块的作用是设定 supercache 页面的缓存信息。没有该模块，IE7用户将只会看见旧页面。','Required to serve compressed supercache files properly.'=>'这是必需的以便能够正确调用缓存文件。','Add the rules yourself. Edit %s.htaccess and find the block of code enclosed by the lines <code># BEGIN WPSuperCache</code> and <code># END WPSuperCache</code>. There are two sections that look very similar. Just below the line <code>%%{HTTP:Cookie} !^.*(comment_author_|%s|wp-postpass_).*$</code> add these lines: (do it twice, once for each section)'=>'添加你自己的规则。编辑 %s.htaccess，找到<code># BEGIN WPSuperCache</code>和<code># END WPSuperCache</code>之间的代码块。有两部分看起来非常相似。在 <code>%%{HTTP:Cookie} !^.*(comment_author_|%s|wp-postpass_).*$</code> 下面，加上这些代码：（做两次，每个部分一次）','Delete the plugin mod_rewrite rules in %s.htaccess enclosed by <code># BEGIN WPSuperCache</code> and <code># END WPSuperCache</code> and let the plugin regenerate them by reloading this page.'=>'删除插件的 mod_rewrite 规则，它们是 %s.htaccess 文件中从 <code># BEGIN WPSuperCache</code> 开始到 <code># END WPSuperCache</code> 结束的代码块，随后请刷新本页来重建规则。','Scroll down the Advanced Settings page and click the <strong>Update Mod_Rewrite Rules</strong> button.'=>'滚动查看高级选项卡，找到并点击 <strong>更新 Mod_Rewrite 规则</strong> 按钮。','Set the plugin to simple mode and enable mobile support.'=>'设置插件为传统模式并且启用手机支持。','Mobile support requires extra rules in your .htaccess file, or you can set the plugin to simple mode. Here are your options (in order of difficulty):'=>'若要对手机用户进行配置，需要额外添加规则到 .htaccess 文件中，或者您启用传统模式。这是您的选择(有些困难)：','The rewrite rules required by this plugin have changed or are missing. '=>'插件需要的重写规则已被更改或者缺失。','Rewrite rules must be updated'=>'重写规则必须被更新','This will have no affect on ordinary users but mobile users will see uncached pages.'=>'这将不会影响电脑用户，但是手机用户将会访问未缓存的页面。','For best performance you should enable "Mobile device support" or delete the mobile rewrite rules in your .htaccess. Look for the 2 lines with the text "2.0\\ MMP|240x320" and delete those.'=>'为了更好的访问体验，您应该启用 "手机设备支持" 或者删除 .htaccess. 文件中的手机重写规则。请查找 "2.0\\ MMP|240x320" 文本并删除它们。','Mobile rewrite rules detected'=>'检测到针对手机的重写规则','You should change the permissions on %s and make it more restrictive. Use your ftp client, or the following command to fix things:'=>'您应该通过 ftp 客户端或者以下命令更改 %s 的权限并确保它被严格限制：','Warning! %s is writeable!'=>'警告！ %s 可被写入！','Dismiss'=>'取消','Garbage collection by this plugin clears out expired and old cached pages on a regular basis. Use <a href="#expirytime">this form</a> to enable it.'=>'这个插件的垃圾回收通过定期清除出过期老的缓存页面。使用 <a href="#expirytime">此表单</a> 启用它。','Warning! Garbage collection is not scheduled!'=>'警告！没有计划进行垃圾回收！','Read-only:'=>'只读：','Writeable:'=>'可写的：','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Changing_File_Permissions">This page</a> explains how to change file permissions.'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Changing_File_Permissions">这个页面</a> 讲述了如何修改文件权限。','A simple way of doing that is by changing the permissions temporarily using the CHMOD command or through your ftp client. Make sure it&#8217;s globally writeable and it should be fine.'=>'最简单的方法就是通过 ftp 客户端使用 CHMOD 命令临时修改文件权限。请确保文件全局可被写入，然后就可以了。','The WP Super Cache configuration file is <code>%s/wp-cache-config.php</code> and cannot be modified. That file must be writeable by the web server to make any changes.'=>'WP Super Cache设置文件<code>%s/wp-cache-config.php</code>无法改写。该文件必须设置为服务器可写才能进行改写。','Read Only Mode. Configuration cannot be changed.'=>'只读模式。设置无法更改。','It appears that mod_rewrite is not installed. Sometimes this check isn&#8217;t 100% reliable, especially if you are not using Apache. Please verify that the mod_rewrite module is loaded. It is required for serving Super Cache static files in expert mode. You will still be able to simple mode.'=>'貌似 mod_rewrite 模块尚未安装。也许情况并不是这样，尤其是当您不使用 Apache 作为服务器程序的时候。请检查 mod_rewrite 模块是否被加载。这对于 Super Cache 的静态文件的调用是必需的。不过您可以使用 PHP 缓存模式或者传统模式运行本插件。','Mod rewrite may not be installed!'=>'Mod rewrite 模块可能未安装！','PHP is compressing the data sent to the visitors of your site. Disabling this is recommended as the plugin caches the compressed output once instead of compressing the same page over and over again. Also see #21 in the Troubleshooting section. See <a href="http://php.net/manual/en/zlib.configuration.php">this page</a> for instructions on modifying your php.ini.'=>'PHP 正在压缩发送到来访者的数据。建议禁用该功能，因为本插件已经缓存了压缩后的输出数据而不是重复压缩多次它们。同时请查看 readme 文件的疑难问题解决部分的第21号问题。查看 <a href="http://php.net/manual/en/zlib.configuration.php">这个页面</a> 以了解配置 php.ini 的介绍。','Zlib Output Compression Enabled!'=>'Zlib 输出压缩已启用！','Cannot continue... fix previous problems and retry.'=>'无法继续... 清修复之前遇到的问题然后重试。','Unfortunately, WordPress cannot find the file wp-cron.php. This script is required for the correct operation of garbage collection by this plugin, WordPress scheduled posts as well as other critical activities.'=>'不幸的是，WordPress 找不到文件 wp-cron.php。此脚本是这个插件进行垃圾收集的正确操所需，WordPress安排文章，以及其他关键的活动。','Please see entry 16 in the <a href="%s">Troubleshooting section</a> of the readme.txt'=>'请查看 readme.txt 中 <a href="%s">疑难问题解决部分</a> 的第16号问题','Your server thinks your hostname resolves to %s. Some services such as garbage collection by this plugin, and WordPress scheduled posts may not operate correctly.'=>'您的服务器认为您的主机解析至 %s。有些服务比如垃圾回收器和定时发布功能将无法正常工作。','Warning! Your hostname "%s" resolves to %s'=>'警告！您的主机 "%s" 被解析至 %s','A custom url or permalink structure is required for this plugin to work correctly. Please go to the <a href="options-permalink.php">Permalinks Options Page</a> to configure your permalinks.'=>'本插件需要正确的自定义链接或者固定链接结构才能正常工作。请前往 <a href="options-permalink.php">固定链接设置</a> 页面进行配置。','Permlink Structure Error'=>'固定链接结构出错','You or an administrator must disable this. See the <a href="http://php.net/features.safe-mode">safe mode manual page</a> for further details. This cannot be disabled in a .htaccess file unfortunately. It must be done in the php.ini config file.'=>'您或者管理员必须禁用该功能。更多信息请访问 <a href="http://php.net/features.safe-mode">PHP 安全模式手册</a> 。很遗憾这个操作不能在 .htaccess 文件中修改，您必须修改 php.ini 文件。','You or an administrator may be able to make it work by changing the group owner of the plugin scripts to match that of the web server user. The group owner of the %s/cache/ directory must also be changed. See the  <a href="http://php.net/features.safe-mode">safe mode manual page</a> for further details.'=>'您或管理员可以通过更改插件脚本的组所有者以使其与Web服务器用户的组所有者相匹配来使其工作。 还必须更改%s/cache/目录的组所有者。 有关详细信息，请参阅<a href="http://php.net/features.safe-mode">安全模式手册页面</a>。','Your server is set up to check the owner of PHP scripts before allowing them to read and write files.'=>'在 PHP 代码读取或者写入文件之前，您的服务器程序将会检查其属主。','You may experience problems running this plugin because SAFE MODE is enabled.'=>'由于启用了安全模式,在插件运行时您可能会遇到问题。','Warning! PHP Safe Mode Enabled!'=>'警告！PHP 安全模式已启用！','Please create %s/wp-cache-config.php from wp-super-cache/wp-cache-config-sample.php'=>'请从 wp-super-cache/wp-cache-config-sample.php 创建 %s/wp-cache-config.php','[%1$s] WP Super Cache GC Report'=>'[%1$s] [%1$s] WP Super Cache 垃圾回收器报告','Cache expiry cron job took more than 30 seconds. You should probably run the garbage collector more often.'=>'缓存到期检查任务已经执行了不少于30秒。您可能需要更经常地运行垃圾回收期。','Cache expiry cron job failed. Job will run again in 10 seconds.'=>'清理到期缓存计划任务执行失败，将会在10秒后重试。','WPTouch plugin detected! Please go to the Supercache plugins page and enable the WPTouch helper plugin.'=>'已检测到 WPTouch 插件！请前往插件设置首页启用 WPTouch 插件支持。','WPTouch support is now %s'=>'WPTouch 兼容%s','Provides support for <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wptouch/">WPTouch</a> mobile theme and plugin.'=>'<a href="https://cn.wordpress.org/plugins/wptouch/">点击查看 WPTouch 的手机主题和插件本身的支持</a>。','WPTouch'=>'WPTouch','Caching has been disabled on this blog on the Network Admin Sites page.'=>'在该博客的站点网络管理页面上缓存功能已被禁用。','Disable'=>'禁用','Enable'=>'启用','Cached'=>'已缓存','Jetpack Mobile Theme support is now %s'=>'Jetpack移动主题支持现在是%s','Provides support for the <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/">Jetpack</a> mobile theme and plugin. PHP caching mode and mobile support will be enabled too.'=>'支持<a href="https://cn.wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/">Jetpack</a>移动主题和插件。PHP缓存模式和移动的支持也将被启用。','Jetpack not found in %s. Install it and enable the mobile theme and this helper plugin to cache visits by mobile visitors.'=>' %s中未找到Jetpack。请安装它并启用移动主题和这一插件，进行移动访问的高速缓存。','Jetpack Mobile Theme'=>'Jetpack 移动主题','Domain Mapping plugin detected! Please go to the Supercache plugins page and enable the domain mapping helper plugin.'=>'已检测到 Domain Mapping 插件！请前往本插件的设置首页启用 Domain Mapping 插件支持。','Domain Mapping support is now %s'=>'Domain Mapping 兼容%s','Provides support for <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-mu-domain-mapping/">Domain Mapping</a> plugin to map multiple domains to a blog.'=>'<a href="https://cn.wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-mu-domain-mapping/">点击查看 Domain Mapping 插件对同主机多站点的支持</a>。','Domain Mapping'=>'Domain Mapping','Warning!'=>'警告!','Bad Behavior support is now %s'=>'Bad Behavior 兼容%s','(Only WPCache caching supported, disabled compression and requires <a href="http://www.bad-behavior.ioerror.us/">Bad Behavior</a> in "%s/plugins/bad-behavior/") '=>'(仅支持传统模式，并且需要禁用压缩以及确保 <a href="http://www.bad-behavior.ioerror.us/">Bad Behavior</a> 插件在 "%s/plugins/bad-behavior/" 目录中) ','Bad Behavior'=>'Bad Behavior','Bad Behaviour not found. Please check your install.'=>'没有找到 Bad Behavior 插件。请检查您的安装。','Update'=>'更新','Awaiting Moderation is now %s'=>'%s现正等待修改','disabled'=>'已禁用','enabled'=>'已启用','Enables or disables plugin to Remove the text "Your comment is awaiting moderation." when someone leaves a moderated comment.'=>'启用或禁用该插件以便移除当新的待审核评论产生时的 "您的评论正在等待审核。" 提示。','Disabled'=>'已禁用','Enabled'=>'已启用','Awaiting Moderation'=>'等待修改','Your comment is awaiting moderation.'=>'您的评论正在等待审核。','Save Changes'=>'保存修改','Skip https URLs to avoid "mixed content" errors'=>'忽略 https 地址以避免 "mixed content" 错误','These <a href="https://www.wikipedia.org/wiki/CNAME_record">CNAMES</a> will be used in place of %1$s for rewriting (in addition to the off-site URL above). Use a comma as the delimiter. For pages with a large number of static files, this can improve browser performance. CNAMEs may also need to be configured on your CDN.<br />Example: %2$s'=>'这些<a href="https://www.wikipedia.org/wiki/CNAME_record">CNAMES</a>将用于代替%1$s进行重写（除了上面的场外网址）。 使用逗号作为分隔符。 对于具有大量静态文件的页面，这可以提高浏览器性能。 可能还需要在CDN上配置CNAMEs。<br />示例：%2$s','Additional CNAMES'=>'附加 CNAME 记录','Excludes something from being rewritten if one of the above strings is found in the URL. Use a comma as the delimiter like this, <code>.php, .flv, .do</code>, and always include <code>.php</code> (default).'=>'如果以上的字符串中有任何一个符合，那么将不会被写入至重写规则中。请使用半角逗号隔开，例如 <code>.php, .flv, .do</code>,，并且无论如何不要删去 <code>.php</code> (默认)。','Exclude if substring'=>'如果是之前有则排除','Directories to include in static file matching. Use a comma as the delimiter. Default is <code>wp-content, wp-includes</code>, which will be enforced if this field is left empty.'=>'匹配静态文件要包含的目录。使用逗号作为分隔符。默认值为<code>wp-content，wp-includes</code>，如果该字段为空则强制执行。','Include directories'=>'包括目录','The new URL to be used in place of %1$s for rewriting. No trailing <code>/</code> please.<br />Example: <code>%2$s</code>.'=>'这个新的URL替换%1$s用来重写，不要用<code>/</code>结尾，<br />例如<code>%2$s</code>。','Off-site URL'=>'Off-site URL','Enable CDN Support'=>'开启 CDN 支持','You can define different CDN URLs for each site on a multsite network.'=>'您可以对多站点中的每个站点定义不同的 CDN 服务地址。','<strong style="color: red">WARNING:</strong> Test some static urls e.g., %s  to ensure your CDN service is fully working before saving changes.'=>'<strong style="color: red">警告：</strong> 请测试一些静态地址比如 %s 以便确保您的 CDN 服务在保存设置前正在工作。','Your website probably uses lots of static files. Image, Javascript and CSS files are usually static files that could just as easily be served from another site or CDN. Therefore, this plugin replaces any links in the <code>wp-content</code> and <code>wp-includes</code> directories (except for PHP files) on your site with the URL you provide below. That way you can either copy all the static content to a dedicated host or mirror the files to a CDN by <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=cdn+origin+pull" target="_blank">origin pull</a>.'=>'您的网站可能使用了大量的静态文件。例如图片、Javascript和CSS这些静态文件通常可以从其他网站或CDN提供服务。因此，该插件将您网站的<code>wp-content</code>和<code>wp-includes</code>目录中的任何链接（PHP文件除外）替换为您提供的URL。这样，您可以将所有的静态内容复制到特定主机上，或者通过<a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=cdn+origin+pull" target="_blank">origin pull</a>将文件镜像到CDN。']];